thread.title: Paul Butcher

author: Paul Butcher
title: Paul Butcher
text: I decided to get a private reg after a lot of thought and searching, when i got in touch with reg transfers they quickly found what i wanted and i bought it. Did not have a clue what was involved in getting my reg so i was very glad to find i need not do anything. The whole process was fast and very well executed, well done to everyone who helped with my purchase.
